Dioxus also supports a special type of Element: Text. Text Elements do not accept children, but rather just string literals denoted with double quotes. rsx! ( "hello world"
) Text Elements can be composed within other Elements: rsx! ( div { h1 { "hello world" } p { "Some body content" } }
