Yes - another macro! However, this one is entirely optional. For internal components, we provide the inline_props macro, which will let you embed your Props definition right into the function arguments of your component. Our title card above would be transformed from: #[derive(Props, PartialEq)]
struct TitleCardProps { title: String,
